═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  Topic 0 [Arthritis]: {RA, RA of knee, Arthritis, OA}
    Strategy 1: is any CUI ancestor of ≥2 others?
      Arthritis is parent of RA and OA → YES
      Pick Arthritis? No — RA has higher IC (14.6 > 8.4)
      Actually: pick the ancestor → Arthritis as grouper,
      but medoid for label.
    Strategy 2: medoid (highest mean cosine to all members)
      RA: mean cosine to others = 0.94
      Arthritis: mean cosine = 0.90
      → RA is medoid → REP = C0003873 (RA)

  Topic 6 [Neurological disorder]: {Seizure, Seizure mgmt, Epilepsy, Headache}
    Strategy 1: Epilepsy is ancestor of Seizure → covers 1 (need 2) → NO
    Strategy 2: medoid
      Seizure: mean cosine to others = 0.72
      Epilepsy: mean cosine = 0.68
      → Seizure is medoid → REP = C0036572 (Seizure)


